{"tid":1590260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正你老母視聽]乜都可以做","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:42:48.000Z","uid":281135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67ee85f0fc7059d4b7942259fbb7ad03d50507e7","tid":1590260,"uid":281135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"一定唔可以搶槍？<br />\n搶槍on99無撚用？<br />\n搶槍俾機會佢射你？<br />\nhi有個男老師無咗隻左眼<br />\nhi有個女FA無咗隻右眼<br />\nhi新屋嶺有十幾個手足俾人打到斷骨<br />\nhi新屋嶺有好多女手足俾人輪姦<br />\nhi太子站仲有幾個手足俾人監生打死<br />\n荃灣跌槍都開實彈<br />\n維園隻鬼都開實彈<br />\n對住火魔法師佢地都舉咗槍<br />\n你覺得離開槍打死人有幾遠？<br />\n點解美國唔會好似香港咁做乜都得？<br />\n因為佢地每個平民都有槍係手<br />\n如果我地有槍係手，會有以上咁多嘢發生？<br />\n如果我搶咗枝槍，你覺得班狗會唔會就住就住，驚唔知幾時俾人一槍爆頭？<br />\n講唔搶槍嘅，自己諗<br />\n<br />\n以上係l4d2心得，見到地下有槍點解唔執，係都要拎住枝棍？點打tank？"},{"pid":"6e83f11abd16463b885f49d64b7f2db653dd7c82","tid":1590260,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"1830dabb5d98d88f912a0912add5d4e410f82787","tid":1590260,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士及死難者<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a